[p 
	"FF04: I/O address used by the RNG for entropy.
	$LF
	"FFD3: RNG byte. Controls type of Pokémon in an encounter, and damage during battle.
	$LF
	"FFD4: RNG byte. Controls Pokémon encounter events, and critical hits.
	$LF
